      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Oliver Uwira</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://chess-tigers.de/index_news.php?id=346&amp;rubrik=1&amp;PHPSESSID=b11203af3eda02c923e993f2f5730ea1\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Uwira_Oliver_2004_HSV.jpg/300px-Uwira_Oliver_2004_HSV.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"387\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/f/f3/Uwira_Oliver_2004_HSV.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Uwira_Oliver_2004_HSV.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Oliver Uwira <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Oliver Uwira</b>,<br />\na German <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FIDE_Master\">FIDE-Master</a> in chess, and computer scientist with a diplom in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business_informatics\">business informatics</a> from the <a href=\"/Darmstadt_University_of_Technology\" title=\"Darmstadt University of Technology\">Darmstadt University of Technology</a> in 2011. As member of the <i>Knowledge Engineering Group</i> headed by <a href=\"/Johannes_F%C3%BCrnkranz\" title=\"Johannes Fürnkranz\">Johannes Fürnkranz</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> , he was involved in the development of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_poker_player#Player_bots\">poker bots</a> <i>AKI-RealBot</i>, <i>mcBotUltra</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> , <i>dpp</i> and <i>akuma</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. Oliver is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine <a href=\"/Kurt\" title=\"Kurt\">Kurt</a>, which had it over the board debut at the <a href=\"/Chess960CWC_2006\" title=\"Chess960CWC 2006\">Chess960CWC 2006</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Uwira&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/104175240058823208048/about\">Hendrik Schaffer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Uwira</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>Limit Texas Hold’em - Einführung in Konzepte menschlicher Strategie</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ke.tu-darmstadt.de/lehre/archiv/ss08/challenge/Ausarbeitungen/Schaffer_Uwira.pdf\">pdf</a> (German</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/104175240058823208048/about\">Hendrik Schaffer</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Uwira</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>TUD Poker Challenge - Einführung in menschliche Strategien</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ke.tu-darmstadt.de/lehre/archiv/ss08/challenge/Folien/Folien-Schaffer_Uwira.pdf\">sildes as pdf</a> (German)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Uwira&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36149\">One step forward again</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Uwira</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 22, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36331\">New Version: Kurt 0.9.2 beta</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Uwira</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 11, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=51248\">New Version: Kurt 0.9.2 beta</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Uwira</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 11, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36516\">Is a querying the hash tables such a huge bottleneck?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Uwira</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 28, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36530\">Open Source with Java or C#</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Uwira</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 29, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a>, <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Uwira&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=4646630\">Uwira, Oliver FIDE Chess Profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/perl/chessplayer?pid=74103\">The chess games of Oliver Uwira</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/index.html\">chessgames.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://revilopedia.blogspot.com/\">Revilopedia</a> blog by Oliver Uwira </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Uwira&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chess-tigers.de/index_news.php?id=346&amp;rubrik=1&amp;PHPSESSID=b11203af3eda02c923e993f2f5730ea1\">Chess Tigers Training Center: Aktuelles vom Hessenschach - Uwira mit +2600 Leistung beim Karl-Mala-Turnier, August 05, 2005, Copyright © 2018 Chess Tigers Training Center GmbH</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ke.tu-darmstadt.de/\">Knowledge Engineering Group</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/%7Epokert/2008/results/\">2008 Poker Bot Competition Summary - 6-Player Texas Hold'em Limit</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/%7Epokert/2009/results/\">2009 Poker Bot Competition Summary</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://tu-darmstadt.academia.edu/OliverUwira\">Oliver Uwira | Technische Universität Darmstadt - Academia.edu</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301152133\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 89/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 198/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5180-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301152133 and revision id 10502\n -->\n"
